  "body": "While looking at some tracing stuff I noticed that the ext auth filter does its own tracing: https://github.com/envoyproxy/envoy/blob/9aa85a314552bffb60c13a6acfd60317eaa3bc14/source/extensions/filters/common/ext_authz/ext_authz_http_impl.cc#L220.\r\n\r\nThis is before we added tracing directly into async client: https://github.com/envoyproxy/envoy/blob/9aa85a314552bffb60c13a6acfd60317eaa3bc14/include/envoy/http/async_client.h#L237\r\n\r\nWe should replace the ext auth specific tracing with that provided by the async client.\r\n\r\ncc @dio ",
